data.description: Desirable Union School District / Darnaby Elementary. Beautifully maintained one story home with so much to offer! Three living areas, including a secluded bonus room that's perfect for work/school at home. Massive kitchen with lots of counter space and cabinets, bright and cheerful sunroom, newer interior and exterior paint on all walls and cabinets, backyard updated in 2020, new faucets and fans in 2020. HVAC 2021. Backyard shed has electricity.
